CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 5, 1966, pg. 1B, reads: "During Intermission - This quintet got together for a bit of fun and conversation during intermission at the Dynamic Danettes Mardi Gras Ball at the Pick- Roosevelt Hotel. Left to right: Mr. and Mrs. Paul Pallard [Pollard], Edward Dorsey, Mr. and Mrs. William Miller."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait from left: Paul Pollard, Mrs. Pollard, Edward Dorsey, Mrs. Miller, and William Miller, posed in Roosevelt Hotel for Danettes Mardi Gras ball
